'''Saudi Arabia''' is an original [[Nations|country]] that was on BitLife in September 2018. Its default cities are the capital, namely Riyadh, along with Jeddah and Mecca.

== Information ==
Being an Islam-based country, female characters in BitLife will wear hijabs when they are adults. This is shared with females in [[Afghanistan]], [[United Arab Emirates]], [[Iraq]],  and [[Iran]]. If a female does not originally have one before emigrating, her emoji will be replaced with one that does. If she emigrates to a non-Islam based country, her hijab may be removed. Female lovers or hook-ups who originate from one of these countries will have her hijab.

If you come out as homosexual, you will be arrested.

Saudi Arabia is along with [[Indonesia]], [[Iran]] and [[Singapore]] that [[Crime|Drug trafficking and drug possession]] is punished by death penalty.

